{"id":52,"date":"2022-03-15T15:19:58","date_gmt":"2022-03-15T14:19:58","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/leahall.fet.creativeschools.co.uk\/uniform\/"},"modified":"2023-06-26T14:21:29","modified_gmt":"2023-06-26T13:21:29","slug":"uniform","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/leahall.fet.ac\/parents\/joining-the-school\/uniform\/","title":{"rendered":"Uniform"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Our year-round school uniform consists of <\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>A dark green jumper or sweatshirt<\/li><li>A white shirt or polo shirt<\/li><li>Black or grey trousers<\/li><li>Black shoes<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Sweatshirts and polo shirts, with the school logo, are available to buy from Brigade Clothing by clicking the link below. However, it is optional to purchase uniform with the school logo.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Order Uniform Online<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.brigade.uk.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"612\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/leahall.fet.ac\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/6\/2022\/06\/image002.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-399\" srcset=\"https:\/\/leahall.fet.ac\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/6\/2022\/06\/image002.png 612w, https:\/\/leahall.fet.ac\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/6\/2022\/06\/image002-300x98.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 612px) 100vw, 612px\" \/><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/www.brigade.uk.com\/\">http:\/\/www.brigade.uk.com<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-file\"><a id=\"wp-block-file--media-78b00844-6c47-4940-b638-789f4cd3b380\" href=\"https:\/\/leahall.fet.ac\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/6\/2022\/06\/Uniform-Guidance.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Uniform Guidance<\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Parents\/Carers are asked to supply their child with a clearly named PE kit and if required as part of the school\u2019s curriculum offer, they may need a swimming costume and towel for swimming sessions.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If parents\/carers feel that their child may require a change of clothes during the school day, the school is happy to keep a spare set of school uniform. A limited amount of clothing is kept in school for emergency purposes. Soiled items of clothing are securely bagged in school and returned to parents\/carers at the end of the day. All clothing should be clearly labelled with the child\u2019s name.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"684\" src=\"https:\/\/leahall.fet.ac\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/6\/2022\/06\/LeaHall052-1024x684.jpg\" alt=\"LeaHall052\" class=\"wp-image-342\" srcset=\"https:\/\/leahall.fet.ac\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/6\/2022\/06\/LeaHall052-1024x684.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/leahall.fet.ac\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/6\/2022\/06\/LeaHall052-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/leahall.fet.ac\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/6\/2022\/06\/LeaHall052-768x513.jpg 768w, https:\/\/leahall.fet.ac\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/6\/2022\/06\/LeaHall052-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/leahall.fet.ac\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/6\/2022\/06\/LeaHall052.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-file\"><a id=\"wp-block-file--media-c4457785-3c7f-4251-a0d5-dd24ed82cce4\" href=\"https:\/\/leahall.fet.ac\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/6\/2022\/10\/Uniform-Policy_2022-2023.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Uniform Policy 2022 2023<\/a><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>There is an official school uniform which we do expect pupils to wear. Our uniforms are chosen to be comfortable, practical, and appropriate.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":301,"parent":47,"menu_order":3,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-52","page","type-page","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry"],"acf":{"sidebar":true,"landing_page":false},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/leahall.fet.ac\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/52"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/leahall.fet.ac\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/leahall.fet.ac\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/leahall.fet.ac\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/leahall.fet.ac\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=52"}],"version-history":[{"count":9,"href":"https:\/\/leahall.fet.ac\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/52\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1061,"href":"https:\/\/leahall.fet.ac\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/52\/revisions\/1061"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/leahall.fet.ac\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/47"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/leahall.fet.ac\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/301"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/leahall.fet.ac\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=52"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}